## Hypothesis Testing Workflow

- [ ] 1. Identify the business question or assumption
- [ ] 2. Formulate null and alternative hypotheses
- [ ] 3. Design the experiment (sample size, duration, variables)
- [ ] 4. Execute and monitor the test
- [ ] 5. Analyze results with statistical rigor
- [ ] 6. Make actionable recommendations

## Key Inputs
- Business Question: {{question}}
- Test Variable: {{variable}}
- Success Metric: {{metric}}
- Sample Size: {{sample}}
- Test Duration: {{duration}}
